  "texts": [
    "There are several cutting-edge innovations in new technologies, including the Internet of 1 3",
    "Things, artificial intelligence, sensors, cloud computing, solar power, Arduino, and big data analytics.",
    "These innovations have the potential to increase productivity and efficiency throughout the entire value chain of agriculture.",
    "They can also boost farmers' incomes, enhance farm productivity, reduce waste, and improve supply-chain efficiency, transparency, and the sustainable use of resources (Bhagat et al. 2019; World Economic Forum 2021; Sinwar et al. 2020; StartUs Insights 2022).",
    "Agritech innovations have been implemented in farming systems to meet the demands of feeding a growing global population."
  ]
}